### **1ï¸âƒ£ Clone the Repository**
```sh
git clone <your-repo-url>
cd <your-project-folder>
```

### **2ï¸âƒ£ Start the Project**
Run the script to build and start all services:
```sh
./readmw.sh
```
(If not executable, run: `chmod +x readmw.sh`)

---

## **Manual Steps (If Needed)**
### **1ï¸âƒ£ Build & Start Docker Containers**
```sh
docker-compose down -v
docker-compose up --build -d
```

### **2ï¸âƒ£ Run Migrations**
```sh
docker-compose exec web python manage.py makemigrations
docker-compose exec web python manage.py migrate
```

### **3ï¸âƒ£ Create Django Superuser (Optional)**
```sh
docker-compose exec web python manage.py createsuperuser
```

### **4ï¸âƒ£ Collect Static Files**
```sh
docker-compose exec web python manage.py collectstatic --noinput
```

### **5ï¸âƒ£ Restart Celery Services**
```sh
docker-compose restart celery_worker
docker-compose restart celery_beat
docker-compose restart flower
```

