---

## **Celery Task Flow**
1ï¸âƒ£ **Django API writes data** â†’ **Stored in MySQL**  
2ï¸âƒ£ **Celery Worker detects new data** â†’ **Syncs it to PostgreSQL**  
3ï¸âƒ£ **Celery Beat periodically checks & fixes unsynced records**  
4ï¸âƒ£ **Flower UI monitors Celery worker status**  

